Jest typings should use latest typescript features to infer mock types. 

Tests in general should be using typed mocks instead of 'any' values.

let spy4: jest.SpyInstance;
spy4 = jest.spyOn(spiedTarget, "returnsString");

let spy4; // let spy4: jest.SpyInstance<string, []>;
